The Rwang Pam stadium in Jos, Plateau State is filled to capacity as Governor Simon Bako Lalong arrived the stadium to flag off his re-election campaign. The governor arrived the stadium in company of the National Chairman of the All Progressives Congress (APC), Comrade Adams Oshiomhole to a cheering crowd of supporters at about 1:26. Oshiomhole is expected to receive decampees from the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) and other political parties. Chairmen of 51 political parties endorse Lalong as he flags off campaign Gov. Lalong, Sen Useni to flag off campaign tomorrow We are only waiting to swear in President Buhari -Lalong